1. make the build directory

  ex) 

   $ mkdir build


2. change the working directory to the build directory

  ex)

   $ cd build


3. run 'cmake'

  $ cmake ${SOURCE_DIR} -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/usr

  ex)

   $ cmake .. -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/usr

   or

   $ cmake ..


4. make & make install

  ex)

   $ make -j 2 && make install

